## Workspace Structure
```
vintage_ai_client/       - Multi-provider AI abstraction (OpenAI, Anthropic)
vintage_blending_core/   - Game similarity algorithms and feature vectors
vintage_build_tools/     - Build-time code generation and analysis
vintage_game_generator/  - Main application with Bevy UI
```

