## AI Client Patterns
```rust
// Use the unified AI client abstraction
use vintage_ai_client::{AiClient, Provider};

let client = AiClient::new(Provider::OpenAI, api_key)?;
let response = client.complete(prompt).await?;
```

## Error Handling
- Use `thiserror` for library error types
- Use `anyhow` in the application crate
- Always provide context with `.context()`

